[quote=“Ooo Java, post:7, topic:83418”][quote author=FastBawlz link=topic=122574.msg1199410#msg1199410 date=1177274210]

That is so crap. Change the gradient map to soft light.

Dont say just soft light… There are many other settings that you should work with… Like overlay, darken, …normal with lowered opacity…Hue , Luminosity…Even though they aren’t as common, they can give some nice outcomes.

–Just advice for everyone…
